{"tid":2517071,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"現時尿兜設計真係好落後","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T05:54:44.000Z","uid":35315,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df4fde9d559a94e8b577d10b6d3a2eecc7fd93ff","tid":2517071,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"男人老狗，去親廁所對住個尿兜屙尿永遠都要面對兩大難題<br />\n第一：尿兜彈尿／水，彈到褲／鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二：尿兜對落地下成日都有一灘混合尿液<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩大原因<br />\n第一：尿會係個尿兜彈返出黎<br />\n第二：廢J屙尿滴滴仔，無得救<br />\n所以我認為改善尿兜設計係最有效嘅方法<br />\n內容用小畫家劣畫，各位巴打見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n普遍尿兜，強調係<strong>普遍尿兜</strong>都係類似以下設計，下巴成兜狀<br />\n巴打們有一條稍有返少少力嘅JJ，即使有足球仔畀你瞄準，尿柱嘅衝擊力都足夠令大大小小嘅尿水珠／水花彈到周圍都係，褲／鞋成日中招<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVzBjfmiJNA1JAha2uXspLs71sXgPeAXs6kLsnMMvYwie?filename=BN8tQOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBN8tQOu.png&h=200ccd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我一直有個迷思，點解尿兜要設計成兜狀，而唔係利用斜角反射減少回彈嘅可能性<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXcW8DeRhAdRYZ4H5cbWBjbscjaV7WGydjBGma9ANXsDj?filename=NVQcxXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVQcxXo.jpg&h=3dc48c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考示範圖，利用反射角度可以將回彈到嘅尿花減至最低程度<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYxTpfLyFu8Jzk4gWYNdPpDwM5Q4TZ3WFPXaaZ4jAqtSx?filename=sLHa36b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLHa36b.png&h=720ead5b&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n申利: 我知個名同個Post 相映成趣，並不代表本人有前列線疾病<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e81549faae1a3eb93c7c7d751a7c7b5bdc99a2a","tid":2517071,"uid":263334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"用水樽屙算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5105790a361ca575eb7644df30a8bd82549a46a3","tid":2517071,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e81549faae1a3eb93c7c7d751a7c7b5bdc99a2a","tid":2517071,"uid":263334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"用水樽屙算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"咁咪成班麻甩佬係個廁所一人揸住一支水樽屙, 屙完仲要倒?<br />\n屌拿星真係拎尿袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938b6781256123ce7a00eadc950c42b40523beec","tid":2517071,"uid":398215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"你on9定咩，沿住條邊屙絕少會彈"},{"pid":"afb96d8ade0ab0fea6c3fe594e46021071a6f8c5","tid":2517071,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"每次睇到呢d post 都好老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見了d 圖想博君一笑，但完全fail<br />\n又唔好意思講出黎"},{"pid":"4e483b41d26f6dd74a740fd394afc4ff815d2374","tid":2517071,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"938b6781256123ce7a00eadc950c42b40523beec","tid":2517071,"uid":398215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"你on9定咩，沿住條邊屙絕少會彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"真心咩? <br />\n我都係沿住條邊屙, 但間唔中都會有細水花彈出黎<br />\n你留意睇就有"},{"pid":"f1e84e620724b1dded52caa185f7187f2227d1e2","tid":2517071,"uid":4724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"我估唔咁設計係考慮沖廁水問題掛<br />\n水黏性有冇高到可以咁設計都沖埋個斜位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff642e54c8914da066a1fb39846c7ca5029fbf3b","tid":2517071,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":